Slater Industries Inc said it planned a15 mln dlr modernization of its Slater Steels Corp Fort Waynespecialty bar division in Indiana.    It said the modernization would involve replacement of theexisting bar mill with a high-speed, quick-change continuousmill. The new facility will lower labor and mill costs andenhance product quality and range, Slater said.    Completion date of the new mill was undisclosed. Reuter&#3;